<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Verify your email — Mishka Den</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; color: #222;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Welcome to Mishka Den, {{ display_name }} 🐻</h1>
    <p>Please verify your email by clicking the link below:</p>
    <p style="margin: 24px 0;">
        <a href="{{ url }}" style="background: #5a3d2b; color: #fff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block;">Verify email</a>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666;">Or copy this URL into your browser:<br><span style="word-break: break-all;">{{ url }}</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666;">This link expires in 24 hours.</p>
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666;">If you didn't sign up, ignore this email — your account isn't active until verified.</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 32px; font-size: 13px; color: #888;">— Mishka, the den mother for your family</p>
</body>
</html>
